@ValidDataPackageId(message="data-package-management.error.data-package.id.not-valid-id") @ValidShadowId(message="data-package-management.error.data-package.id.pattern") public class DataPackage extends AbstractShadowableRdcDomainObject implements eu.dzhw.fdz.metadatamanagement.datapackagemanagement.domain.projection.DataPackageSubDocumentProjection
A data package contains all metadata of a DataAcquisitionProject. It will get a DOI (Digital Object Identifier) when the DataAcquisitionProject is released.
